我们被叫到了瞭望塔，有紧急情况。

342
00:28:36,173 --> 00:28:39,886
- Great. I'll head to the tower and... - Damian. Damian...
-太好了。我要去塔楼然后..。-达米安.达米安。

343
00:28:40,553 --> 00:28:45,391
Only the titans have been called to the watchtower, and well...
只有巨人被召唤到了瞭望塔，而且……

344
00:28:46,392 --> 00:28:49,103
You've never officially been inducted, so...
你还没有正式入伍过，所以...

345
00:28:49,186 --> 00:28:50,466
An oversight, I'm sure.
我肯定，这是个疏忽。

346
00:28:50,730 --> 00:28:52,875
I'll head over, swear on whatever you have handy and...
我会过去，用你手边的任何东西发誓...

347
00:28:52,899 --> 00:28:54,567
No! No.
不是的！不是的。

348
00:28:56,235 --> 00:28:58,696
Damian, we've taken a vote.
达米安，我们已经投票了。

349
00:28:59,322 --> 00:29:00,740
We don't want you on the team.
我们不想让你加入我们的队伍。

350
00:29:02,241 --> 00:29:05,411
You're just too violent,
你就是太暴力了，

351
00:29:05,995 --> 00:29:07,955
and don't do well with others.
不要和别人相处得很好。

352
00:29:08,581 --> 00:29:10,958
We are a team. We need to work as one,
我们是一个团队。我们需要团结一致，

353
00:29:11,042 --> 00:29:13,294
and I'm sorry to say this,
我很抱歉这么说，

354
00:29:13,377 --> 00:29:16,714
but you don't care for anyone but yourself.
但你不关心任何人，除了你自己。

355
00:29:18,090 --> 00:29:20,593
- Sorry. - Sorry? Don't be sorry.
-对不起.-你说什么？不要抱歉。

356
00:29:20,968 --> 00:29:22,261
The only reason I've come around
我来这里的唯一原因

357
00:29:22,345 --> 00:29:24,805
is 'cause my father, Batman, begged me to.
是因为我父亲蝙蝠侠求我这么做。

358
00:29:25,264 --> 00:29:28,643
And why would I want to hang out with a bunch of justice league wannabes anyway?
我为什么要和一群追求正义联盟的人混在一起呢？

359
00:29:29,018 --> 00:29:31,771
- Damian, I'm just... - Good luck on failing without me.
-达米安，我只是...-祝你在没有我的情况下失败。

360
00:29:42,782 --> 00:29:44,502
Hey, I was wondering if you could show me...
嘿，我在想你能不能给我看一下...

361
00:29:46,994 --> 00:29:47,995
You have a cow?
你养了一头牛？

362
00:29:49,246 --> 00:29:50,331
Of course I have a cow.
我当然有一头奶牛。

363
00:29:52,625 --> 00:29:54,293
When was the last time you milked her?
你上次给她挤奶是什么时候？

364
00:29:55,753 --> 00:29:56,796
Milked her?
给她挤奶？

365
00:29:56,879 --> 00:30:00,424
Yeah. You have to milk it, it's a cow.
嗯。你得给它挤奶，它是头奶牛。

366
00:30:00,549 --> 00:30:03,177
Listen, I can milk her, dude. It's fine, it's no problem.
听着，我可以给她挤奶，伙计。很好，没问题。

367
00:30:03,260 --> 00:30:04,679
Over my dead body.
绝不允许。

368
00:30:04,762 --> 00:30:08,808
I don't need some small town hick telling me how to take care of a cow.
我不需要小镇上的乡巴佬来教我怎么照顾一头牛。

369
00:30:09,392 --> 00:30:11,602
I'm the grandson of the demon's head.
我是恶魔头颅的孙子。

370
00:30:12,311 --> 00:30:14,397
I've killed more people than you'll ever meet.
我杀的人比你见过的都多。

371
00:30:14,772 --> 00:30:17,733
So leave my cow and my cave alone!
所以离我的牛和我的洞穴远点！

372
00:30:22,905 --> 00:30:25,241
Hey, don't look at me, he's your friend.
嘿，别看我，他是你的朋友。

373
00:30:27,284 --> 00:30:28,644
Green arrow, is that you?
绿箭，是你吗？

374
00:30:29,578 --> 00:30:30,579
Yes. Sorry.
是。抱歉的。

375
00:30:30,997 --> 00:30:32,498
We 're having trouble with the comms.
我们的通讯出了点问题。

376
00:30:32,790 --> 00:30:35,501
Whatever hit the watchtower, knocked out a couple of transmitters,
不管是什么击中了瞭望塔，摧毁了几个发射器，

377
00:30:35,626 --> 00:30:36,961
but we're almost up and running.
但我们马上就要上线了。

378
00:30:37,086 --> 00:30:39,422
Understood. Keep me updated as to your progress.
明白了。随时向我汇报你们的进展情况。

379
00:30:39,922 --> 00:30:41,799
Of course, Batman. Watchtower out.
当然了，蝙蝠侠。瞭望塔完毕。

380
00:30:43,676 --> 00:30:45,112
- Something's off. - Something's off.
-有点不对劲。-有点不对劲。

381
00:30:45,136 --> 00:30:47,847
Let me drop Jonathan at home and we'll head to the watchtower,
让我把乔纳森放在家里，然后我们去瞭望塔，

382
00:30:47,930 --> 00:30:49,432
see what's really going on.
看看到底是怎么回事。

383
00:30:50,766 --> 00:30:51,600
Hey, dad.
嘿，爸爸。

384
00:30:51,684 --> 00:30:53,394
- Hey. Ready to go? - Yep.
-嘿.准备好了吗，-准备好了

385
00:30:55,479 --> 00:30:58,065
Uh, Mr. Batman, you have an awesome cave.
蝙蝠侠先生你有一个很棒的洞穴。

386
00:30:58,190 --> 00:30:59,525
It was really great to meet you.
见到你真的很高兴。

387
00:30:59,650 --> 00:31:01,235
Oh! And, uh, here.
噢!还有，呃，给你。

388
00:31:08,200 --> 00:31:09,200
How did it go?
结果如何？（后来呢？）？

389
00:31:09,368 --> 00:31:10,786
As well as can be expected.
正如可以预期的那样。

390
00:31:11,078 --> 00:31:12,538
Mom, I met Batman!
妈妈，我见过蝙蝠侠了！

391
00:31:13,080 --> 00:31:14,206
He's so...
他太..。

392
00:31:15,458 --> 00:31:18,252
- Uh, broody? - No, I was gonna say cool.
-嗯，布鲁迪？-不，我是想说酷.

393
00:31:18,586 --> 00:31:20,379
All right, kiddo, time for bed.
好了，孩子，该睡觉了。

394
00:31:21,088 --> 00:31:23,549
But, dad, we should go on patrol, right?
但是，爸爸，我们应该去巡逻，对吗？

395
00:31:25,259 --> 00:31:28,554
I mean, you never know what bad guys are up to in Smallville.
我是说，你永远不知道坏人在小镇干嘛。

396
00:31:28,846 --> 00:31:31,432
Then lucky them, because you need some sleep.
那就算他们走运了，因为你需要休息。

397
00:31:32,058 --> 00:31:33,059
You have school tomorrow.
你明天要上学。

398
00:31:40,107 --> 00:31:41,984
I'm leaving a present on your nightstand.
我在你的床头柜上放了一件礼物。

399
00:31:42,359 --> 00:31:45,029
It'll help you on your first step to being a superhero.
它将帮助你迈向成为超级英雄的第一步。

400
00:31:45,446 --> 00:31:46,446
Thanks, dad.
谢谢你，爸爸。

401
00:31:46,947 --> 00:31:48,074
I love you guys.
我好爱你们。

402
00:31:48,783 --> 00:31:50,367
- Good night. - Love you, too.
-晚安.-我也爱你。

403
00:31:50,993 --> 00:31:51,993
Good night.
晚安。

404
00:31:55,247 --> 00:31:56,415
I have to go back out.
我得回去了。

405
00:31:56,624 --> 00:31:58,751
Something strange is going on at the watchtower.
瞭望塔上发生了一些奇怪的事情。

406
00:31:59,335 --> 00:32:01,670
- It's the night for that, I suppose. - What do you mean?
-我想，今晚是时候了。-你是什么意思？

407
00:32:01,754 --> 00:32:03,065
I've been getting these wild tips
我一直在得到这些疯狂的提示

408
00:32:03,089 --> 00:32:05,508
from contacts all throughout central and South America.
来自中美洲和南美洲各地的联系人。

409
00:32:05,966 --> 00:32:07,593
The crime rate has plummeted.
犯罪率直线下降。

410
00:32:07,885 --> 00:32:09,303
Well, that's good, right?
嗯，那很好，对吧？

411
00:32:09,386 --> 00:32:11,222
You would think. But when I say "plummeted,"
你可能会想。但当我说“暴跌”时

412
00:32:11,305 --> 00:32:13,933
I mean, there's no more crime.
我是说，再也没有犯罪了。

413
00:32:14,266 --> 00:32:16,227
Not even a purse snatching being reported.
甚至连抢钱包的报告都没有。

414
00:32:16,435 --> 00:32:17,875
We should go investigate.
我们应该去调查一下。

415
00:32:18,354 --> 00:32:19,730
I'll go get my cape.
我去拿我的披风。

416
00:32:23,484 --> 00:32:25,986
- We did good. - Yeah, we sure did.
-我们做得很好。-是的，我们确实是这样做的.

417
00:32:40,292 --> 00:32:44,380
Watchtower. Batman, security code 0x-11 docking.
瞭望塔。蝙蝠侠，安全代码0x-11正在对接。

418
00:33:12,700 --> 00:33:13,742
It's quiet.
这里很安静。

419
00:33:13,826 --> 00:33:15,578
- Let's do a full sweep. - On it.
-让我们做一个全面的检查。-在这上面.

420
00:33:21,458 --> 00:33:22,960
We have to get out of here. Now!
我们得离开这里。现在!

421
00:33:36,223 --> 00:33:37,516
Some present.
一些礼物。

422
00:33:42,271 --> 00:33:44,023
So that's why you couldn't hit anything.
这就是你什么都打不中的原因。

423
00:33:44,857 --> 00:33:45,983
You're blind.
你是个盲人。

424
00:33:46,901 --> 00:33:47,943
Whatever, Melvin.
管他呢，梅尔文。

425
00:33:48,777 --> 00:33:51,071
Listen, can't see Kent,
听着，我看不到肯特，

426
00:33:51,405 --> 00:33:54,867
I think you need to apologize for losing our game.
我想你应该为输掉我们的比赛道歉。

427
00:33:55,159 --> 00:33:57,703
"Our game"? You aren't even on our team.
“我们的游戏”？你甚至都不在我们队里。

428
00:33:57,786 --> 00:33:59,580
Ooh!
哦！

429
00:34:00,372 --> 00:34:02,333
I could be on the team if I wanted to.
如果我想的话，我可以加入球队。

430
00:34:02,791 --> 00:34:07,796
But only nerds with good grades are allowed to play, and I'm no nerd.
但只有成绩好的书呆子才能玩，我不是书呆子。

431
00:34:08,047 --> 00:34:09,089
Yeah.
嗯。

432
00:34:09,715 --> 00:34:11,508
Wait. I'm on the team.
等。我是球队的一员。

433
00:34:11,592 --> 00:34:14,136
Shut it, Kenny. You know what?
闭嘴，肯尼。你猜怎么着？

434
00:34:14,678 --> 00:34:17,097
Maybe I'll just make Jonathan here do my homework,
也许我会让乔纳森帮我做作业

435
00:34:17,473 --> 00:34:20,517
and then I'll join the team and we'll never lose again.
然后我会加入球队，我们再也不会输了。

436
00:34:20,643 --> 00:34:22,394
In your dreams.
在你的梦里。

437
00:34:25,564 --> 00:34:26,607
Oh!
噢!

438
00:34:32,321 --> 00:34:33,906
Super-strength.
超强的力量。

439
00:34:35,449 --> 00:34:36,700
You okay, Melvin?
你还好吗梅尔文？

440
00:34:37,326 --> 00:34:38,953
Of course I'm okay.
我当然很好。

441
00:34:39,411 --> 00:34:40,621
I must have tripped.
我一定是绊倒了。

442
00:34:42,206 --> 00:34:45,793
Like I said, how about an apology?
就像我说的，道歉怎么样？

443
00:34:46,043 --> 00:34:48,921
Only when your mom apologizes for your face.
只有当你妈妈为你的脸道歉的时候。

444
00:34:51,465 --> 00:34:53,759
Did you just... did you...
你刚才是不是..。你有没有。

445
00:34:54,343 --> 00:34:55,719
You're in for it now, Kent!
你现在有麻烦了，肯特！

446
00:34:56,053 --> 00:34:58,013
Do your worst, Melvin, the moron.
尽你最大的努力，梅尔文，这个笨蛋。

447
00:35:04,061 --> 00:35:05,729
Who needs the teen titans?
谁还需要青少年巨人呢？

448
00:35:06,355 --> 00:35:08,023
Teen titans.
青少年巨人。

449
00:35:08,357 --> 00:35:09,900
Stupid name anyway.
不管怎么说，这个名字很蠢。

450
00:35:10,442 --> 00:35:11,527
I'll make my own team.
我会组建我自己的团队。

451
00:35:12,194 --> 00:35:14,488
Yeah, maybe we'll even lead an assault on titans tower.
是啊，也许我们甚至会领导一场对泰坦斯塔的进攻。

452
00:35:14,863 --> 00:35:16,907
Show them how well we can work together.
让他们看看我们能合作得有多好。

453
00:35:35,592 --> 00:35:37,428
You tried to sneak up on me?
你想偷偷靠近我？

454
00:35:37,594 --> 00:35:39,680
My mother taught me how to avoid that in the crib.
我母亲在婴儿床上教我如何避免这种情况。

455
00:35:41,598 --> 00:35:44,310
Father, are you, okay?
父亲，你还好吗，好吗？

456
00:36:05,497 --> 00:36:06,540
What the...
这是什么.。

457
00:36:44,661 --> 00:36:47,081
Father, don't make me hurt you.
父亲，别逼我伤害你。

458
00:36:47,706 --> 00:36:48,791
It is time.
是时候了。

459
00:37:01,595 --> 00:37:04,765
Father, please, snap out of it.
父亲，拜托，振作起来吧。

460
00:37:15,067 --> 00:37:17,152
The southern hemisphere has been taken over.
南半球已经被占领。

461
00:37:17,736 --> 00:37:19,136
We 7! Be at the tipping point soon,
我们7个！很快就到了临界点，

462
00:37:19,446 --> 00:37:21,281
and this planet will be ours.
这个星球将是我们的。

463
00:37:21,532 --> 00:37:22,616
And the others?
其他人呢？

464
00:37:22,741 --> 00:37:24,284
They've been taken care of.
他们已经被照顾好了。

465
00:37:24,785 --> 00:37:26,412
All threats have been infected.
所有威胁都已被感染。

466
00:37:27,329 --> 00:37:29,748
- It is time. - It is time.
-是时候了。-是时候了。

467
00:37:57,609 --> 00:37:59,153
They've all been infected.
他们都被感染了。

468
00:37:59,862 --> 00:38:01,572
No one's left, but...
没有人离开，但是...

469
00:38:04,741 --> 00:38:06,076
Oh, really?
哦，真的吗？

470
00:38:08,162 --> 00:38:10,122
Yes, yes, I'll save him, okay?
是的，是的，我会救他的，好吗？

471
00:38:10,873 --> 00:38:11,999
But only 'cause you asked.
但只是因为你问了。

472
00:38:12,666 --> 00:38:15,002
Honestly, Jonathan, I expect more from you.
说实话，乔纳森，我对你的期望更高。

473
00:38:15,085 --> 00:38:17,337
And I'm sure your mother and father do, too.
我相信你的父母也是如此。

474
00:38:17,546 --> 00:38:20,382
- But Melvin... - You know Melvin has issues.
-但是梅尔文...-你知道梅尔文有问题.

475
00:38:20,507 --> 00:38:23,343
People like that need more sympathy and Patience.
像这样的人需要更多的同情和耐心。

476
00:38:23,469 --> 00:38:26,513
And maybe, if you have the heart, they deserve friendship.
也许，如果你有诚意，他们理应得到友谊。

477
00:38:26,722 --> 00:38:28,557
- You're kidding me. - No, I'm not.
-你在开玩笑吧.-不，我没有.

478
00:38:28,807 --> 00:38:31,894
People like Melvin, they're hurt. They lash out.
像梅尔文这样的人，他们很受伤。他们猛烈抨击。

479
00:38:32,102 --> 00:38:34,062
But you take the time to get to know them,
但你要花时间去了解他们，

480
00:38:34,313 --> 00:38:36,607
well, they'll be the most loyal friend you'll ever know.
他们会是你所知道的最忠诚的朋友。

481
00:38:36,690 --> 00:38:38,525
Thanks, but no thanks.
谢谢，但不用了。

482
00:38:38,692 --> 00:38:39,860
Just think about it.
你好好想想看。

483
00:38:40,736 --> 00:38:42,821
Now, if you were any other kid, you'd be suspended.
现在，如果你是其他孩子，你会被停职。

484
00:38:42,946 --> 00:38:45,908
But as it is, I put in a call to your mother and she said,
但事实是，我给你母亲打了个电话，她说，

485
00:38:45,991 --> 00:38:49,453
and I quote, "I'll be there to make sure he never does that again."
我引用他的原话：“我会在那里确保他永远不会再这样做。”

486
00:38:50,078 --> 00:38:51,718
I hope you learned your lesson, young man.
我希望你吸取了教训，年轻人。

487
00:38:52,331 --> 00:38:53,331
Yeah, um,
是啊，嗯，

488
00:38:53,415 --> 00:38:56,627
you know what, principal Cunningham, you're right, lesson learned.
你知道吗，坎宁安校长，你说得对，吸取了教训。

489
00:38:56,752 --> 00:38:58,879
You really are amazing at your job.
你真的很擅长你的工作。

490
00:38:59,004 --> 00:39:01,507
I promise, no more trouble from me.
我保证，不会再有我的麻烦了。

491
00:39:03,884 --> 00:39:05,594
Damn, I am good at my job.
妈的，我很擅长我的工作。

492
00:39:11,266 --> 00:39:13,101
Really? Isn't that a little obvious?
真的？这是不是有点太明显了？

493
00:39:13,310 --> 00:39:16,021
I was actually a fan before I found out.
在我发现这件事之前，我其实是个粉丝。

494
00:39:16,313 --> 00:39:19,191
You know who was my... You know what? It doesn't matter.
你知道谁是我的..。你猜怎么着？无所谓。

495
00:39:19,358 --> 00:39:20,358
What are you doing here?
你在这里干嘛？

496
00:39:20,692 --> 00:39:22,069
Aliens are taking over the globe.
外星人正在占领地球。

497
00:39:22,444 --> 00:39:23,444
Come on, farm boy.
来吧，农场男孩。

498
00:39:23,737 --> 00:39:26,907
- We've got to go save our dads. - What? How?
-我们得去救我们的爸爸们-什么？多么?

499
00:39:27,157 --> 00:39:28,951
- What happened to your face? - Uh...
-你的脸怎么了？-呃...

500
00:39:29,034 --> 00:39:31,286
Actually, another power kicked in today, so...
实际上，今天又来了一股力量，所以...

501
00:39:31,370 --> 00:39:32,496
It was super-strength.
这是超强的表现。

502
00:39:32,579 --> 00:39:35,791
But evidently, super-strength doesn't mean invulnerability to punches, so...
但显然，超强并不意味着击打无懈可击，所以...

503
00:39:36,291 --> 00:39:37,291
So you punched yourself?
所以你打了自己？

504
00:39:37,459 --> 00:39:40,629
Just please stay on point. What is this about aliens?
请不要拘泥于主题。外星人是怎么回事？

505
00:39:41,213 --> 00:39:42,607
That's right, you're a little slow.
是的，你有点慢。

506
